{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_52_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 行きたい場所があるんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――神社境内併設のカフェ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Cafe inside the shrine grounds",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、境内にこんな本格的なカフェがあるとは\n周りは静かだし、案外いいもんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t expect such a stylish cafe to be inside the shrine grounds.\nIt’s quiet around here—it’s actually really nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優に聞いた時は私も驚きました\n調べてみたら、最近増えているらしいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised too when Yu told me about it.\nI looked it up—apparently‚ these kinds of cafes have been popping up lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.7099772135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……神社、どこを見ても素敵でしたね\nお守りも沢山種類があって迷いましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… Every part of that shrine was beautiful‚ wasn’t it?\nThere were so many kinds of charms that I couldn’t decide which to pick…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "このレースで出来たお守り、本当に可愛いです\n{user}さんはどれを授けてもらいましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this lace charm is just so adorable.\nWhich one did you get‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3912018139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うちの神社は商売繁盛より縁結びにご利益があるから\n……って言われたから、縁結びのお守りにしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They told me this shrine is more about blessings for relationships than business success…\n…so I chose a charm for good relationships.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3887980143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、きっといいお仕事の縁に恵まれますよ\n新しいお仕事、私も楽しみにしてますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I’m sure you’ll be blessed with great work relationships.\nI’m looking forward to your next project‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.914127032
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.914127032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの神社、手水舎も綺麗でしたね\nお花が水面に一杯浮かべてあって、ロマンチックでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That shrine earlier—the purification fountain was beautiful too.\nAll those flowers floating on the water… it was so romantic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "調べてみたら『花手水』って言うみたいだな\n俺も驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I looked it up—it’s called hanachōzu‚ apparently.\nI was surprised too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5579359214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "京都のいろんな神社やお寺でやっているそうです\n午後は花手水を巡ってみるのもいいかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like a lot of shrines and temples in Kyoto do it.\nMaybe we could visit a few of them this afternoon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、その前に行きたい場所があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But before that‚ there’s somewhere I want to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5131513119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どこに行きたいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where do you want to go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1706343492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7988883098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "市内の、レンタル着物のお店に行きたいんです\nせっかくの京都ですから、着物で観光してみたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to visit a kimono rental shop in the city.\nWe’re in Kyoto‚ after all—I’d love to try sightseeing in a kimono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "着物や小物の種類も豊富で、着付けもしてくれる\nいいお店を優に教えてもらったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu told me about a really nice shop that has a great selection of\nkimonos and accessories‚ and they help with dressing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.742696039
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "着たら写真送って、とも言われていて……\n{user}さんも、その……どうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She also told me to send her a photo once I’ve put it on…\nSo‚ um… {user}-san‚ would you… like to come with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺は遠慮しておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I think I’ll pass.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2390000424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2539433242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、ですか……\nせっかく、一緒に京都に来てるのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see…\nEven though we came to Kyoto together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.4990904888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依？　いや……あの、そうだな……\nいい思い出になるだろうし、やっぱり行ってもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rui? Uh… well‚ you know…\nIt’d make for a nice memory‚ so… maybe I will go after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だからその……元気を出してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ um… cheer up‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5284785987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.9307916881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、いいんですか？　嬉しいです！\nじゃあ、一緒に写真も撮りましょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ really? I’m so happy!\nThen let’s take some photos together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.0710860174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "急に元気になったな……分かった分かった\n瑠依は着物が似合いそうだし、いい写真になりそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You perked up fast… alright‚ alright.\nI bet kimonos would really suit you‚ Rui. It’ll make for great pictures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8813583296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "に、似合うだなんて、そんな……\nまだ着物を選んでもないのに、その……少し照れます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-suit me? Oh‚ come on…\nI haven’t even picked one yet‚ but… you’re making me blush.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7390941836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.4181381783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まったら、行きましょう\n{user}さんの着物は私が選びますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let’s get going.\nI’ll pick out your kimono‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、えっと……私の着物は\n{user}さんが選んでくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ um… for my kimono—\nCould you choose it for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.0561423859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、俺が……センスに自信がないな……\nじゃあせめて、一緒に選ぶ、でもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ me? I’m not sure I’ve got the sense for that…\nThen… how about we pick them together‚ at least?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.8333312988,
      "sfxList": []
